item.title: Fix add file to gitignore not filtered
item.description: <pre><br>git rm -r --cached .<br>git add .<br>git commit -m 'clear git cache'<br>git push<br></pre>

item.title: How to make pull request or contribution on github
item.description: <h2>Contribution Tutorial</h2><ol> <li>Fork it (git clone https://github.com/name/repo)</li> <li>Create your feature branch (git checkout -b my-new-feature)</li> <li>Commit your changes (git commit -am 'Add some feature')</li> <li>Push to the branch (git push origin my-new-feature)</li> <li>Create new Pull Request</li></ol>
